---
title: Thai-Inspired Curry Chicken Noodle Soup  with Dark Meat Chicken, Coconut Milk, Bok Choy & Lime
description: This coconut curry soup warms our hearts (and our palates!). Tonights’ soup features ground pork, slurpable ramen noodles, fresh bok choy and cabbage, and all the craveable coconut curry and chili flavors. Curl up in your favorite spot because you’re about to be warmed from head to toe with this delicious, spicy soup.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66fc18e5f7f79adb61ec7c08-0ec7a828.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66fd90f2966ea033d562ccba-en-US.pdf
